<div>
    <div>
        <p class="py-1 flex flex-row "><span class="font-semibold inline-block sm:basis-24 basis-1/5">Score</span> <span class="basis-4/5"> An overal score for your page. Ranging from 0 to 100</span></p>
        <p class="py-1 flex flex-row"><span class="font-semibold inline-block sm:basis-24 basis-1/5">Speed</span> <span class="basis-4/5"> Seconds to load everything visible on the users screen</span></p>
        <p class="py-1 flex flex-row"><span class="font-semibold inline-block sm:basis-24 basis-1/5">FCP</span> <span class="basis-4/5"> First Contentful Paint. This is the first time a users sees something on the screen</span></p>
        <p class="py-1 flex flex-row"><span class="font-semibold inline-block sm:basis-24 basis-1/5">TBT</span> <span class="basis-4/5"> Total Blocking Time. Time the website is blocked after the first element is vissible</span></p>
        <p class="py-1 flex flex-row"><span class="font-semibold inline-block sm:basis-24 basis-1/5">LCP</span> <span class="basis-4/5"> Largest Contentful Paint. This is when all vissible elements of the page are loaded</span></p>
        <p class="py-1 flex flex-row"><span class="font-semibold inline-block sm:basis-24 basis-1/5">TTI</span> <span class="basis-4/5"> Time to interactive. This is the time it takes for the user to be able to interact with the page</span></p>
        <p class="py-1 flex flex-row"><span class="font-semibold inline-block sm:basis-24 basis-1/5">CLS</span> <span class="basis-4/5"> Cumulative Layout Shift . This is the amount page elements change size and posistion while loading. Lower is better</span></p>
        <p class="py-1 flex flex-row"><span class="font-semibold inline-block sm:basis-24 basis-1/5">Size</span> <span class="basis-4/5"> Total size of the webpage.</span></p>
    </div>
